title: Tarot
desc:
- <:tarot:1106300551525826661> Cards can be played on top of the number corresponding to the card it’s based off of (The Fool can be played on 0s, The Magician can be played on 1s, ect.)
- If a <:tarot:1106300551525826661> Card has a number that’s not on a regular Uno card, then they can be played on Wild cards
- <:tarot:1106300551525826661> cards take the color and number of whatever card they are played on.
